title: You’re Doing Amazing Sweetie: A Kardashian Recap Show | It Was All a Stream
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer and Zack Peter return to breakdown another week with the Kardashians in Episode 3. The pair focus in on Kris’s trip to the dispensary (03:00), Kim’s not-so-vegan dinner with her team (11:00), Kendall’s first Prada show (34:00), and much more.
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Zack Peter
Producer: Devon Renaldo
Associate Producer: Jonathan Kermah
